Search for Reports and Dashboards in Lightning Experience

When using the report and dashboard search in Lightning Experience, look for a report by name. To refine your results, sort or search within a selected folder.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Essentials, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions
Available in: Enhanced Folder Sharing

Search doesn't find partial strings within a longer word or number except at the start of the word or number. A word or number starts at the beginning of the field label or following a space. For example:

Searching on “commun” finds “Edge Communications” but searching on “dge” or “cation” doesn’t.
Searching on “12” finds “Leads Report 12” but not “Leads Report-12”.
